    "description": "<br>你发现自己置身于平行的赛博朋克世界，<strong>掷骰</strong>能决定一切。得找到完美骰子，才能重获自由意志。但完美骰子真的存在吗？还是你永远无法逃出生天？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>骰牌并用：</strong> 组合特殊牌组和强化牌组的骰子，达到1+1＞2的效果。使用特殊骰子的能力，将随机性最小化：可复制或移除牌面，重新掷骰，或融合多个骰子！</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/fac4fc41fc0d14c051f41890037e0627.poster.avif?t=1720830526\" width=612 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/fac4fc41fc0d14c051f41890037e0627.webm?t=1720830526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/fac4fc41fc0d14c051f41890037e0627.mp4?t=1720830526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>无法预测的敌人：</strong> 敌人也掷骰，运气也时好时坏。但如果所有掷骰结果如他们所愿，那你就没那么好运了，特别是当你的牌组不能灵活构建的时候。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/6d5ffca82ed82bd60866a86c50e74cec.poster.avif?t=1720830526\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/6d5ffca82ed82bd60866a86c50e74cec.webm?t=1720830526\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/6d5ffca82ed82bd60866a86c50e74cec.mp4?t=1720830526\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>没有绝对的策略：</strong> 你无法每次都用同一种策略取得成功。需要不断调整、试验不同卡牌、骰子、各类能力的组合，找到最优解。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398430/extras/d60ac7a47374b989272d310c6bd0471c.poster.avif?t=1720830526\" width=60